Resolve internal references in an MSData object.

For an MSData object using a SpectrumListSimple to hold Spectrum objects in memory, these references will be resolved as well.

File-backed SpectrumList implementations using lazy evaluation of a Spectrum need to call resolve(spectrum, msd) before returning it to the client.
